          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">How to Arrange a Custom Wānanga</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">For Schools & Community Groups</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
                <li>Minimum 8 participants for custom workshops</li>
                <li>Can be tailored to curriculum needs</li>
                <li>Flexible scheduling including holidays</li>
